{
  "book": 18,
  "chapter": 13,
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“My eyes have seen all this, my ears have heard and understood it. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "“My eyes have seen all this, my ears have heard and understood it."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "What you know, I also know; I am not inferior to you. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "What you know, I also know; I am not inferior to you."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But I desire to speak to the Almighty and to argue my case with God. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But I desire to speak to the Almighty and to argue my case with God."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "You, however, smear me with lies; you are worthless physicians, all of you! "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "You, however, smear me with lies; you are worthless physicians, all of you!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "If only you would be altogether silent! For you, that would be wisdom. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "If only you would be altogether silent! For you, that would be wisdom."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Hear now my argument; listen to the pleas of my lips. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Hear now my argument; listen to the pleas of my lips."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Will you speak wickedly on God’s behalf? Will you speak deceitfully for him? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Will you speak wickedly on God’s behalf? Will you speak deceitfully for him?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Will you show him partiality? Will you argue the case for God? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Will you show him partiality? Will you argue the case for God?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Would it turn out well if he examined you? Could you deceive him as you might deceive a mortal? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Would it turn out well if he examined you? Could you deceive him as you might deceive a mortal?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He would surely call you to account if you secretly showed partiality. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He would surely call you to account if you secretly showed partiality."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Would not his splendor terrify you? Would not the dread of him fall on you? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Would not his splendor terrify you? Would not the dread of him fall on you?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Your maxims are proverbs of ashes; your defenses are defenses of clay. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Your maxims are proverbs of ashes; your defenses are defenses of clay."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“Keep silent and let me speak; then let come to me what may. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "“Keep silent and let me speak; then let come to me what may."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Why do I put myself in jeopardy and take my life in my hands? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Why do I put myself in jeopardy and take my life in my hands?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Though he slay me, yet will I hope in him; I will surely defend my ways to his face. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Though he slay me, yet will I hope in him; I will surely defend my ways to his face."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Indeed, this will turn out for my deliverance, for no godless person would dare come before him! "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Indeed, this will turn out for my deliverance, for no godless person would dare come before him!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Listen carefully to what I say; let my words ring in your ears. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Listen carefully to what I say; let my words ring in your ears."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Now that I have prepared my case, I know I will be vindicated. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Now that I have prepared my case, I know I will be vindicated."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Can anyone bring charges against me? If so, I will be silent and die. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Can anyone bring charges against me? If so, I will be silent and die."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“Only grant me these two things, God, and then I will not hide from you: "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "“Only grant me these two things, God, and then I will not hide from you:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Withdraw your hand far from me, and stop frightening me with your terrors. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Withdraw your hand far from me, and stop frightening me with your terrors."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Then summon me and I will answer, or let me speak, and you reply to me. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Then summon me and I will answer, or let me speak, and you reply to me."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "How many wrongs and sins have I committed? Show me my offense and my sin. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "How many wrongs and sins have I committed? Show me my offense and my sin."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Why do you hide your face and consider me your enemy? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Why do you hide your face and consider me your enemy?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Will you torment a windblown leaf? Will you chase after dry chaff? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Will you torment a windblown leaf? Will you chase after dry chaff?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For you write down bitter things against me and make me reap the sins of my youth. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For you write down bitter things against me and make me reap the sins of my youth."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "You fasten my feet in shackles; you keep close watch on all my paths by putting marks on the soles of my feet. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "You fasten my feet in shackles; you keep close watch on all my paths by putting marks on the soles of my feet."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "You fasten my feet in shackles; you keep close watch on all my paths by putting marks on the soles of my feet."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“So man wastes away like something rotten, like a garment eaten by moths. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "“So man wastes away like something rotten, like a garment eaten by moths."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}